<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link516294" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=516294&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F366269-having-read-day-of-the-triffids-and-the%2Fanswers%2F516294-a-chrysalis-is-a-stage">flag</a>
</div>
