  <div class="friendReviews elementListBrown" >
    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_719674570" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/719674570" />
    <a title="Bionic Jean" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/19300421-bionic-jean"><img alt="Bionic Jean" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1586709362p2/19300421.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/719674570?book_show_action=true">Sep 14, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Bionic Jean" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Bionic Jean" href="/user/show/19300421-bionic-jean">Bionic Jean</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780708981313" href="/book/show/925925.The_Chrysalids">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/19300421-bionic-jean?shelf=read-authors-u-z">read-authors-u-z</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/19300421-bionic-jean?shelf=sf-speculative">sf-speculative</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer719674570" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7498830108584572520">I love this book! It affects me every time I read it, or listen to/watch an adaptation of <b>The Chrysalids</b>. The depiction of a post-nuclear world, where a tiny minority of telepaths are pitted against the general population of religious bigots is pure Wyndham. He takes just a small step away, presents a &quot;What if?&quot; scenario, and proceeds to show human behaviour in all its aspects, warts and all.</span>
  <span id="freeText7498830108584572520" style="display:none">I love this book! It affects me every time I read it, or listen to/watch an adaptation of <b>The Chrysalids</b>. The depiction of a post-nuclear world, where a tiny minority of telepaths are pitted against the general population of religious bigots is pure Wyndham. He takes just a small step away, presents a "What if?" scenario, and proceeds to show human behaviour in all its aspects, warts and all.</span>
  <a data-text-id="7498830108584572520" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


